import { ally, enemy } from "../dataSet";

export const unit1 = {

    level:5,
    unit:1,
    name:"God's blade",
    team:ally,
    maxHp:100,
    hp:100,
    damage:100,
    width:100,
    height:100,
    location:null,
    createTime:4,
    upperBody:"대기",
    lowerBody:"대기",
    hitRange:40,
    attackRange:40,
    attackSpeed:(40 * 26),
    preDelay:(33.333 * 8),
    postDelay:(33.333 * 18)
};

    location:null,

    hitRange:40,
    attackRange:200,
    attackSpeed:400,
};
export const unit3 = {
    id:null,
    level:5,
